# open-infra console — local dev env. Copy to .env to override.
# All CLUSTER-SPECIFIC values come from the BFF's /api/config at runtime,
# so there is nothing secret here. This only affects the local dev proxy.

# Where `npm run dev` proxies /api (the open-infra Go BFF). Default:
# VITE_BFF_TARGET=http://localhost:8080
